The paper deals with image processing and specifically with image retargeting, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a new algorithm for seam-carving, which is a technique used in graphics and image processing (cs.GR). The paper uses measures to assess the quality of the retargeted images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also involves optimization techniques to control the distribution of seams, which is a common theme in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
